	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Which games use:
<br />
<br />-MMC1's static bank at $8000? ($8000.2 = 0)
<br />-MMC3's static bank at $8000? ($8000.6 = 1)
<br />
<br />Thanks

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


