	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There are numerous MMC3 games that use the alterrnate PRG bankswitching mode, including SMB3.  The feature is designed to make it possible to bankswitch DPCM sound samples, which must begin in the $C000-FFFF range (APU limitation).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


